{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Noga is my third game as a solo indie developer. It's a single-player story-based  game in first-person, with shooting and driving mechanics. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You are the sole survivor of an alien attack on a military outpost where your friend was kidnapped. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embark on a long and dangerous journey to try to save him and yourself in a world that has suddenly turned upside down and become a death trap.<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2515490/extras/jump600.gif?t=1736874166\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As the story unfold you will discover the truth behind the alien invasion and the forces involved in it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> The story progresses in a world infested with aliens of various types, spaceships, mercenaries and people hiding and trying to survive.  <br>You must fight for your life and the lives of the companions you have collected along the way, upgrade your weapons and vehicles, learn new skills, and investigate the events that led to the invasion. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2515490/extras/ram600.gif?t=1736874166\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game takes place in Israel and goes through different places from the snowy north to desert south.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Main features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">First person control.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fighting with ranged and melee weapons, and with car-mounted machine guns.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Inventory system and crafting.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Branching dialogues in NPCs' conversations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Player character customization.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Stats, perks, and skills to develop as you level up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Vehicle upgrades in workshops.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Local and global map with fast travel points.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game's story and characters are fictional and any connection between them and real-life events is strictly coincidental.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game has been in development since 2022. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2515490/extras/explode600.gif?t=1736874166\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2515490/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736874166","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2515490/page.bg.jpg?t=1736874166","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2515490/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736874166","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2515490/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736874166","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":"This Game may contain content not appropriate for all ages, or may not be appropriate for viewing at work."},"demos":[{"appid":3432740,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Noga is my third game as a solo indie developer. It's a single-player story-based  game in first-person, with shooting and driving mechanics. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You are the sole survivor of an alien attack on a military outpost where your friend was kidnapped. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embark on a long and dangerous journey to try to save him and yourself in a world that has suddenly turned upside down and become a death trap.<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2515490/extras/jump600.gif?t=1736874166\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As the story unfold you will discover the truth behind the alien invasion and the forc